MPI Util --simple python MPI functions using Intel MPI and pthread


1.HOW TO COMPILE: (supporting Intel mpiicc for now)

    make debug

2.HOW TO RECOMPILE:

    make remake

3.HOW TO USE: 

    Must run with 'mpirun -bootstrap slurm -n NUM_OF_NODES -ppn WORK_PER_NODE COMMAND_TO_RUN', if MPI is needed
    Put MPI_Util.py and mpi_util.so under the same directory
    Import functions from MPI_Util
    See MPI_Util.py for details

Credits:

